(
<figureCitation id="B1BEC3B6AC1F3B702E4DD7A2FD0AAAEB" box="[612,682,1486,1511]" captionStart="FIGURE 8" captionStartId="25.[151,250,1893,1915]" captionTargetBox="[186,1424,234,1848]" captionTargetId="figure@25.[151,1436,193,1872]" captionTargetPageId="25" captionText="FIGURE 8. Type specimens of S. purpurascens: lectotype m (A) and paralectotype f (B); S. planum: lectotype m (C) and paralectotype f (D); S. macrophallicum: holotype m (E) and allotype f (F); S. minimum lectotype m (G); S. affine lecototype m (H) (Scale bars = 1 cm)." httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/804200/files/figure.png" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Fig. 8</figureCitation>
