B) from 
<collectingCountry id="51929FA3AC1F3B702850D7A2FB6EAAEB" box="[1145,1230,1486,1511]" name="Mexico" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Mexico</collectingCountry>
(
<collectorName id="8470BAE5AC1F3B7028CBD7A3FA31AAEB" box="[1250,1425,1486,1511]" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">V. Charpentier</collectorName>
); designation: Kevan (1960, unpublished results); location: 
<collectingRegion id="EB4111D1AC1F3B702F37D79EFCC4A907" box="[798,868,1522,1547]" country="Germany" name="Berlin" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Berlin</collectingRegion>
Zoological Museum (BZM), 
<collectingRegion id="EB4111D1AC1F3B702899D79EFB59A907" box="[1200,1273,1522,1547]" country="Germany" name="Berlin" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Berlin</collectingRegion>
, 
<collectingCountry id="51929FA3AC1F3B70292AD79FFACDA907" box="[1283,1389,1523,1547]" name="Germany" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Germany</collectingCountry>
. We were able to examine only the external morphology of this material. 
<emphasis id="1BF10321AC1F3B702F8FD47AFB23A923" box="[934,1155,1558,1583]" italics="true" pageId="24" pageNumber="25">Additional material</emphasis>
: 
<elevation id="A2A83800AC1F3B7028BDD47AFB7AA923" box="[1172,1242,1558,1583]" metricMagnitude="2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.59" pageId="24" pageNumber="25" unit="m" value="459.0">
